        <div class="addon-price">$50</div>
        <p>I’ll build and optimize your profile so your business is ready to show up in local Google searches.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Businesses Choose Blossom Social</h2>
      <p class="section-subtext">
        Everything is designed to keep your business active, visible, and easy to find online.
      </p>

      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h4>More Local Visibility</h4>
          <p>Stay active on Google and social media so potential customers can find and trust your business.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h4>Consistent Content</h4>
          <p>Keep your pages updated without having to think of every post yourself.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h4>Affordable Monthly Support</h4>
          <p>Get help managing your online presence at a price made for small businesses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-box">
        <h2 class="section-title">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p>Message Blossom Social to ask about setup, monthly management, or current pricing.</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:8564192473">856-419-2473</a></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:clevy1209@gmail.com">clevy1209@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p><strong>Facebook:</strong> Blossom Social Co.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 Blossom Social. Built for small business growth.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
